message.text:
Sealing the deal and celebrating growth and collaboration!

The Memorandum of Understanding (MOU) signing ceremony between FEU ITHM and Youth for Tourism and Hospitality was held last September 9, 2025, at the Alfredo Reyes Hall, with the organizations’ aim to further expand and strengthen the future of tourism through combined advocacy and goals of both institutions.

The ceremonial signing is a prelude to the upcoming Y4TH International Conference in November which will unite the academic institutions and other industry players to showcase their competencies in the tourism industry.

Let’s take a moment to look back at the highlights of the event graced by 𝗗𝗿. 𝗛𝗮𝗿𝗼𝗹𝗱 𝗕𝘂𝗲𝗻𝗼 (Dean), 𝗗𝗿. 𝗖𝗵𝗿𝗶𝘀𝗱𝗶𝗲 𝗧𝗼𝗻𝗴𝗼𝗹  (Department Chair, Tourism Management) 𝗠𝗿. 𝗝𝗼𝗵𝗻 𝗣𝗼𝗻𝗰𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗼 𝗔𝗹𝗺𝗲𝗱𝗮  (President, UP AITAA ) 𝗗𝗿. 𝗠𝗮𝗿𝗶𝗮 𝗖𝗿𝗶𝘀𝗲𝗹𝗱𝗮 𝗕𝗮𝗱𝗶𝗹𝗹𝗮 (Treasurer, UP AITAA), other ITHM academic managers, and other Y4TH representatives.

#MOUSigning
#FEUITHM 
#FEU97th
#FEUandY4THCollaboration
#EVENTURA

Caption by: Elaine Babiano
Captured by: Ashlee Madrideo, Kristine Petallano, Zach Dela Cruz
Pubmat by: Lara Sarate

message.text:
Sealing the deal and celebrating growth and collaboration!

The Memorandum of Understanding (MOU) signing ceremony between FEU ITHM and Youth for Tourism and Hospitality was held last September 9, 2025, at the Alfredo Reyes Hall, with the organizations’ aim to further expand and strengthen the future of tourism through combined advocacy and goals of both institutions.

The ceremonial signing is a prelude to the upcoming Y4TH International Conference in November which will unite the academic institutions and other industry players to showcase their competencies in the tourism industry.

Let’s take a moment to look back at the highlights of the event graced by 𝗗𝗿. 𝗛𝗮𝗿𝗼𝗹𝗱 𝗕𝘂𝗲𝗻𝗼 (Dean), 𝗗𝗿. 𝗖𝗵𝗿𝗶𝘀𝗱𝗶𝗲 𝗧𝗼𝗻𝗴𝗼𝗹  (Department Chair, Tourism Management) 𝗠𝗿. 𝗝𝗼𝗵𝗻 𝗣𝗼𝗻𝗰𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗼 𝗔𝗹𝗺𝗲𝗱𝗮  (President, UP AITAA ) 𝗗𝗿. 𝗠𝗮𝗿𝗶𝗮 𝗖𝗿𝗶𝘀𝗲𝗹𝗱𝗮 𝗕𝗮𝗱𝗶𝗹𝗹𝗮 (Treasurer, UP AITAA), other ITHM academic managers, and other Y4TH representatives.

#MOUSigning
#FEUITHM 
#FEU97th
#FEUandY4THCollaboration
#EVENTURA

Caption by: Elaine Babiano
Captured by: Ashlee Madrideo, Kristine Petallano, Zach Dela Cruz
Pubmat by: Lara Sarate

Let’s take a moment to look back at the highlights of the event graced by 𝗗𝗿. 𝗛𝗮𝗿𝗼𝗹𝗱 𝗕𝘂𝗲𝗻𝗼 (Dean), 𝗗𝗿. 𝗖𝗵𝗿𝗶𝘀𝗱𝗶𝗲 𝗧𝗼𝗻𝗴𝗼𝗹  (Department Chair, Tourism Management) 𝗠𝗿. 𝗝𝗼𝗵𝗻 𝗣𝗼𝗻𝗰𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗼 𝗔𝗹𝗺𝗲𝗱𝗮  (President, UP AITAA ) 𝗗𝗿. 𝗠𝗮𝗿𝗶𝗮 𝗖𝗿𝗶𝘀𝗲𝗹𝗱𝗮 𝗕𝗮𝗱𝗶𝗹𝗹𝗮 (Treasurer, UP AITAA), other ITHM academic managers, and other Y4TH representatives.
